<div class="howitworksbanner">So, how does Snowball work?</div>
<p class="howitworksintro">Quite simply, we help you find & amplify your brand advocates</p>
<div class="ultimatecenter">


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num1.png"/>
Create your Snowball Page
</h2>
<p>
A Snowball page is designed for you to connect with your most passionate fans. Startups might use it to run a brand ambassador program. Authors, artists, and musicians might use it to run a fan club. The choice is yours. 
</p>
</div>



<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num2.png" "align:left" />
Invite Fans to Connect
</h2>
<p>
Share your Snowball page on Facebook, Twitter, your website and other online outlets. Fans who are passionate about your brand will connect with you because they want to support you. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num3.png"/>
Empower Fans to Promote</h2>
<p>
Your goal is to get fans to spread your message. You can easily do this on Snowball by publishing actions for your fans to take. Actions can include tweeting about an upcoming event, sharing a promotion on Facebook, composing a blog post, attending an event or referring a friend, among others.  
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num4.png"/>
Track the Results
</h2>
<p>
Every action your fans take is tracked. You can see who your most active and influential advocates are at any time. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num5.png"/>
Rewards!
</h2>
<p>
Show your most influential advocates that you appreciate their support by giving them cool stuff like access to special events and exclusive offers. 
</p>
